## 7. Functional Requirements (Summary)

Full FR identifiers in prior section; abbreviated here for reference.

- **CALM-01–05:** `@finos/calm` is sole schema authority. Palette derived from package. `$schema` URI stored per document. Sidecar uses FINOS `validate()`. Invalid docs blocked at save.
- **STUDIO-01–06:** Bidirectional canvas/JSON sync (500ms debounce). Auto-save 30s. 12 archetype seeds. Node-level version diff.
- **MARKET-01–04:** ES hybrid BM25 + HNSW search. `calm_node_labels` from CALM `nodes[]`. Shareable filter URLs. 3-pattern comparison.
- **WORK-01–04:** Fork creates `DERIVED_FROM` edge. Node binding in `bound_systems`. Drift score on every save. 7 export formats.
- **GOV-01–04:** PG state machine. 4 automated pre-checks on submission. Canvas annotation pins. Append-only audit log.
- **DEV-01–06:** Scaffold validates before generating. OAS3 from connects. Terraform per service node. K8s stubs. Bcrypt API keys. Signed webhook delivery.
- **QUAL-01–04:** Quality score on every save. 4 subscores. Improvement suggestions. Optional quality gate.

