## 8. Non-functional Requirements

| Attribute | Target |
|---|---|
| Availability | 99.5% on K8s. RTO < 30 min. RPO < 1 hour. |
| Performance | ES search P95 < 400ms. Canvas save P95 < 600ms. CALM validation < 200ms. |
| Scalability | 200 concurrent sessions. HPA on FastAPI pods. |
| Security | LDAP bind + JWT HS256 (8h, httpOnly cookie). TLS at cloud LB. Encrypted PVCs. |
| Auditability | Append-only `audit_log`. Actor, action, entity, timestamp, payload on every state change. |
| Data residency | All stores inside customer's cluster. No external egress for core operations. |
| Accessibility | WCAG 2.1 AA. Keyboard navigable. Screen reader compatible. Both light and dark themes. |

