## 9. Data Architecture

### FalkorDB — graph schema (key nodes and relationships)
```
(:Pattern)  calm_json, calm_yaml, calm_schema_uri, domain, pattern_type, status, quality_score
(:Instance) calm_json, bound_systems, drift_score
(:Variation) delta_json
(:Collection) (:CustomNodeType) (:Author) (:Team) (:Org)

DERIVED_FROM { drift_score, last_checked }
SUPERSEDES  OWNED_BY  AUTHORED_BY  INCLUDED_IN  VARIANT_OF  BELONGS_TO
```

### Elasticsearch — `calm_patterns_{org_id}`
```
name, description (text/BM25)
calm_node_labels[], compliance_tags[] (keyword)
quality_score (float)  created_at (date)
embedding (dense_vector 384-dim HNSW)
```

### PostgreSQL — governance and platform metadata
Tables: `orgs`, `teams`, `users`, `role_mappings`, `governance_workflows`, `governance_comments`, `api_keys`, `api_key_usage`, `webhooks`, `webhook_deliveries`, `audit_log` (append-only), `es_sync_status`, `search_zero_results`.

