## 10. Infrastructure

### Docker Compose — three stores only
```yaml
services:
  falkordb:       image: falkordb/falkordb:latest    port: 6379
  elasticsearch:  image: elasticsearch:8.13.0        port: 9200
  postgres:       image: postgres:16-alpine           port: 5432
```

### Local development — run on system
Start all FastAPI services with `uvicorn` and the Node.js validator with `node server.js` directly. A `Makefile` provides `make start-all`, `make start-{service}`, `make stop-stores`, `make migrate`.

### Kubernetes — production
Deployments (HPA) for all FastAPI services. `pattern-svc` has `calm-validator` as a sidecar container. StatefulSets for FalkorDB (primary + replica), Elasticsearch (3 nodes), PostgreSQL. Single LoadBalancer Service on gateway. Kustomize overlays for dev and prod.

